            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1678204779354-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sushi rice</strong> with the <strong>edamame salad</strong>, <strong>Asian-style</strong> <strong>basa goujons</strong> and <strong>ginger & coriander mayo</strong> to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
